summary: Simple mod with Dual Sheath Redux meshes for Project AHO (only 3 weapons).
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]This mod contains DSR meshes for [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90276]Project AHO[/url]. Just install this archive and update "Dual Sheath Redux Patch.esp".

Included meshes for: Controller (Snippy staff), Staff of Elements and Ancient Dwarven Sword.

All credits to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/47591538]Haem Projects[/url] and [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1267569]Neovalen[/url]![/size]
author: Meridiano
